description: This Chainlink VRF common Chukcha purrs with a rating of 40, and a multiplier of 3x. It has a total score of 120, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Leverage for North, Stringalong for East, Nine Lives for South, and 1 for West. Chukcha has the personality suit of quant. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/30403-67911-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Chukcha [120 Votes, Common]
